These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, eggplant, lettuce
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, canadian, dutch
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating lettuce##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the dutch is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Food   | eggplant     | asparagus | lettuce |
| Nationality   | dutch  | turkish    | canadian      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
House: art-deco, victorian, modern
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, subway, airplane
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the modern house is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person eating kale is the person driving the subway##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the victorian house and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| House   | victorian     | modern     | art-deco      |
| Transport   | airplane  | subway | taxi |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daffodil, amaryllis
3 different games are played: chess, domino, mah-jongg
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Flower          | azalea  | amaryllis     | daffodil     |
| Game           | mah-jongg | chess  | domino   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, juice
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
House: art-deco, colonial, modern
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the person drinking mirinda and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Beverage     | mirinda    | juice  | cola |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| House   | modern | art-deco     | colonial      |

