.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, skiing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, november, january
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the fan of gospel and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | climbing | skiing |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Birthday           | november     | march       | january     |

