.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, zinnia
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
City: hannover, berlin, hamburg
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who growszinnia is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who growsazalea and the owner of the horse##2
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower          | azalea | bellflower | zinnia    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| City   | hannover   | berlin     | hamburg        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

