.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
City: hannover, nizza, prague
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
House: craftsman, tower, townhouse
1. the tower house is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person traveling to prague and the craftsman house##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| City          | prague      | nizza   | hannover |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| House     | townhouse         | tower  | craftsman       |

