.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, rowing
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, orange-climbing
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, orange
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's sport is rowing##2
5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Sport      | lacrosse       | badminton      | rowing      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | orange-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Color   | amber     | orange          | apricot       |

