.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bluemaster, game
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, fishing
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Cigar          | bluemaster   | montecristo      | game     |
| Hobby   | fishing  | card-games      | drawing |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi        | bike     |

