There are 3 different nationalities: german, malaysian, russian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
2. the malaysian is between the german and the person who likes chestnut##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the russian##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the german##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Color       | chestnut       | coral       | mauve    |
| Nationality         | russian | malaysian | german |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

