The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
City: rome, venice, liverpool
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
4. the person traveling to venice is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | poppy     | balloon-flower | aconite      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| City   | rome | venice    | liverpool     |

