3. the wooden house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the security-guard and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the person who's hobby is reading is the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Job           | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard |
| Hobby   | puzzles     | filmmaking        | reading         |
| House   | colonial  | wooden    | ranch-style        |

