There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, singing, filmmaking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, punk, trance
1. the person drinking water is between the fan of punk and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the fan of trance##1
5. the person eating garlic is the fan of punk##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water          | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Hobby           | singing | filmmaking | hiking         |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | trance    | punk      |

