There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing, basketball
1. the german is between the person who's sport is basketball and the egyptian##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice  | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Sport     | basketball      | surfing   | ice-hockey |

