2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating plum##1
3. the person driving the ship is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person eating plum and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Food           | mango   | avocado   | plum |
| Transport   | ship | van   | scooter     |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b      | salsa    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

