.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, sailing
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, videographer, freelancer
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the freelancer##1
2. the videographer is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the mechanic is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the videographer is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is cycling and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | lacrosse | sailing     | cycling        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Job   | videographer        | mechanic       | freelancer      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

