.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, russian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, writer, pilot
1. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the analyst##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the analyst##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the chinese##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the pilot and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality        | russian      | mexican | chinese |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Job   | analyst          | writer     | pilot       |

 